caption.title: Cumulative results of Ovitraps in Madeira Island.
caption.p: Annual cumulative number of eggs reported across the island from all the ovitraps, as reported in the Entomological panel bulletins (PEnt_RAMW52/2019, in Portuguese) of the Institute of Health Administration, IP-RAM (IASAÃšDE IP-RAM). Entomological year starts from week 10. Graphs shows cumulative number of eggs for week 10, 2012 to week 52, 2019, with each entomological year represented in a different line color. Adapted from Institute of Health Administration, IP-RAM [ 34].
